title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Landing challenges - Isafjordur
description:
In this video I will show you how I approached the Isafjordur landing challenge and landed successfully on the runway. The first few tries I both landed not in the blue mark and to much to the right. The 3rd and 4th time I improved that piece but there is still some work to do.
